translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ガシャケィラ選手はんも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gashakeira is also

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 順番さえ違えば優勝が狙えた器や。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a contender who could have aimed for the championship if only the draw order had been different.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一回戦とは思えん高レベルな戦いやったな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a high-level match you wouldn't expect from a first round."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「白熱した試合を見せてくれた両選手に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Both fighters who showed us an intense battle,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客からは自然と拍手が送られました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: naturally received applause from the audience."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ａブロック四戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "A Block, fourth match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケーちゃんＶＳ四天王・土の近藤」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kē-chan VS Four Heavenly Kings: Kondo of Earth"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「気は優しくて力持ち、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gentle-spirited and strong,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 四天王一の防御力を誇る近藤選手でしたが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kondo, boasting the greatest defense among the Four Heavenly Kings,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとその上を行く選手が現れました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but surprisingly, a player even surpassing him appeared."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは謎のリスさんことケーちゃん選手。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That is the mysterious Mr. Squirrel, Kē-chan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただのリスにも関わらずその防御力はピカイチ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though just a simple squirrel, his defensive power is top-notch."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どーんな攻撃を食らっても平然とするんやから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No matter what kind of attack he takes, he remains calm,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もうすごい、なんてもんやないね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it's more than amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異常と言ってもいいくらいや」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You could even say it's abnormal."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一時間かけてもかすり傷一つつかない様に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even after an hour, not a single scratch was visible,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 心が折れた近藤選手が自らギブアップしました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kondo, having his spirit broken, gave up himself."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ダークホースって奴やね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's what you call a dark horse.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まさかただのリスが勝つなんて」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who would have thought a mere squirrel would win?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ただケーちゃんの方から
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However, Kē-chan didn't make any attacks,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 攻撃がなかったんは少し気になるね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and that is a bit concerning.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そっちは苦手なんかな？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maybe he's not good at offense?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでも持久戦に持ち込まれると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But even so, when it comes to a battle of endurance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 相手は嫌な筈ですよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the opponent must hate it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これからの戦いに注目ですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's pay close attention to the upcoming matches."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし……どこかで見た気がするような……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But... somehow I feel like I've seen him somewhere before..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ｂブロック三戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "B Block, third match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラフレシア頭巾ＶＳ四天王・水のサイハテ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rafflesia Hood VS Four Heavenly Kings: Saihate of Water"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「四天王一の知力と魔法力を誇る魔法剣士、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The magical swordsman boasting the highest intellect and magical power among the Four Heavenly Kings,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 水のサイハテ選手の登場です」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Player Saihate of Water appears."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「女性ファンの黄色い声援が印象的やったね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The loud cheers from female fans were quite impressive."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを相手取るは年齢、性別、戦闘方法、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Opposing him is a player whose age, gender, and fighting style

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全てが謎に包まれている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are all shrouded in mystery,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頭巾をかぶったラフレシア頭巾選手」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the player known as Rafflesia Hood who wears a hood."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そのラフレシア頭巾選手が頭巾を取ると、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "When Rafflesia Hood took off the hood,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 会場に無茶苦茶な悪臭が漂い、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: an outrageous stench spread throughout the venue,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サイハテ選手、為す術なく気絶！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Saihate player, helpless, fainted!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「会場のお客さん224名も中毒になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "224 audience members were poisoned

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とんでもない災害に包まれ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: engulfed in an outrageous disaster,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 会場は一時パニックとなりました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the venue temporarily went into panic."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えげつなぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's brutal..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ｂブロック四戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "B Block, fourth match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミスターＸＶＳ死にかけ博士」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mr. X VS Dying Doctor"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「死にかけ博士は五年連続出場の常連者、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The Dying Doctor is a regular competitor, appearing five years in a row,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 事前インタビューでは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and in a pre-match interview,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今年こそは優勝をとその意気込みも熱いです」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he expressed strong determination to win the championship this year."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「元気な爺さんやね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "He's a lively old man."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを相手取るは不吉に現れた、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Opposing him is a mysterious figure who appeared ominously,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全身をローブで包んだ謎の人物、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a mysterious person completely wrapped in a robe,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミスターＸ選手です」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mr. X player."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これまた経歴、年齢、性別、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Again, biography, age, and gender,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラフレシア頭巾選手と同様、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: like Rafflesia Hood player,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 謎に包まれてるって、なんやそんなばっかか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are all shrouded in mystery—what is it with so many like that?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一方やる気満々死にかけ博士！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Meanwhile, the Dying Doctor is highly motivated!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 時間をかける気はないと言わんばかりに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: as if to say he doesn't intend to waste time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 試合開始直後から切り札のタコデビルに変身！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he transformed into his trump card, the Octo Devil, right after the match started!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「八本の腕から繰り出される連続攻撃を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The continuous attacks unleashed from eight arms

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しのぎきるんは至難の業や。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are extremely difficult to withstand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これは決まったかと思ったんやけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought this was it for sure, but..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかーし！　その直後！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But—! Immediately after that!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ガシャケィラ選手はんも
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gashakeira is also

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 順番さえ違えば優勝が狙えた器や。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a contender who could have aimed for the championship if only the draw order had been different.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一回戦とは思えん高レベルな戦いやったな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It was a high-level match you wouldn't expect from a first round."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「白熱した試合を見せてくれた両選手に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Both fighters who showed us an intense battle,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 観客からは自然と拍手が送られました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: naturally received applause from the audience."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ａブロック四戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "A Block, fourth match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケーちゃんＶＳ四天王・土の近藤」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kē-chan VS Four Heavenly Kings: Kondo of Earth"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「気は優しくて力持ち、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Gentle-spirited and strong,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 四天王一の防御力を誇る近藤選手でしたが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kondo, boasting the greatest defense among the Four Heavenly Kings,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとその上を行く選手が現れました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but surprisingly, a player even surpassing him appeared."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それは謎のリスさんことケーちゃん選手。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That is the mysterious Mr. Squirrel, Kē-chan.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ただのリスにも関わらずその防御力はピカイチ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though just a simple squirrel, his defensive power is top-notch."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「どーんな攻撃を食らっても平然とするんやから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No matter what kind of attack he takes, he remains calm,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もうすごい、なんてもんやないね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: it's more than amazing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 異常と言ってもいいくらいや」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You could even say it's abnormal."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一時間かけてもかすり傷一つつかない様に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Even after an hour, not a single scratch was visible,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 心が折れた近藤選手が自らギブアップしました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kondo, having his spirit broken, gave up himself."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ダークホースって奴やね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's what you call a dark horse.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まさかただのリスが勝つなんて」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Who would have thought a mere squirrel would win?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ただケーちゃんの方から
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "However, Kē-chan didn't make any attacks,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 攻撃がなかったんは少し気になるね。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and that is a bit concerning.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そっちは苦手なんかな？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Maybe he's not good at offense?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それでも持久戦に持ち込まれると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But even so, when it comes to a battle of endurance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 相手は嫌な筈ですよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the opponent must hate it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これからの戦いに注目ですね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let's pay close attention to the upcoming matches."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし……どこかで見た気がするような……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But... somehow I feel like I've seen him somewhere before..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ｂブロック三戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "B Block, third match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラフレシア頭巾ＶＳ四天王・水のサイハテ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rafflesia Hood VS Four Heavenly Kings: Saihate of Water"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「四天王一の知力と魔法力を誇る魔法剣士、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The magical swordsman boasting the highest intellect and magical power among the Four Heavenly Kings,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 水のサイハテ選手の登場です」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Player Saihate of Water appears."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「女性ファンの黄色い声援が印象的やったね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The loud cheers from female fans were quite impressive."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを相手取るは年齢、性別、戦闘方法、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Opposing him is a player whose age, gender, and fighting style

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全てが謎に包まれている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are all shrouded in mystery,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頭巾をかぶったラフレシア頭巾選手」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: the player known as Rafflesia Hood who wears a hood."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そのラフレシア頭巾選手が頭巾を取ると、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "When Rafflesia Hood took off the hood,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 会場に無茶苦茶な悪臭が漂い、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: an outrageous stench spread throughout the venue,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サイハテ選手、為す術なく気絶！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and Saihate player, helpless, fainted!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「会場のお客さん224名も中毒になる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "224 audience members were poisoned

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: とんでもない災害に包まれ、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: engulfed in an outrageous disaster,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 会場は一時パニックとなりました」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and the venue temporarily went into panic."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「えげつなぁ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's brutal..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「Ｂブロック四戦目、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "B Block, fourth match,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミスターＸＶＳ死にかけ博士」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mr. X VS Dying Doctor"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「死にかけ博士は五年連続出場の常連者、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The Dying Doctor is a regular competitor, appearing five years in a row,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 事前インタビューでは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and in a pre-match interview,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今年こそは優勝をとその意気込みも熱いです」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he expressed strong determination to win the championship this year."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「元気な爺さんやね」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "He's a lively old man."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それを相手取るは不吉に現れた、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Opposing him is a mysterious figure who appeared ominously,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全身をローブで包んだ謎の人物、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: a mysterious person completely wrapped in a robe,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ミスターＸ選手です」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Mr. X player."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「これまた経歴、年齢、性別、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Again, biography, age, and gender,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ラフレシア頭巾選手と同様、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: like Rafflesia Hood player,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 謎に包まれてるって、なんやそんなばっかか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are all shrouded in mystery—what is it with so many like that?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「一方やる気満々死にかけ博士！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Meanwhile, the Dying Doctor is highly motivated!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 時間をかける気はないと言わんばかりに、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: as if to say he doesn't intend to waste time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 試合開始直後から切り札のタコデビルに変身！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he transformed into his trump card, the Octo Devil, right after the match started!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「八本の腕から繰り出される連続攻撃を
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The continuous attacks unleashed from eight arms

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: しのぎきるんは至難の業や。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: are extremely difficult to withstand.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: これは決まったかと思ったんやけど……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I thought this was it for sure, but..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかーし！　その直後！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "But—! Immediately after that!"
